gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Suns 130, Kings 125
gameRecap.excerpt: Kevin Durant (28 points, 11 rebounds, 11-17 FG), Devin Booker (25 points, nine assists) and the Suns outlast De’Aaron Fox (40 points, nine rebounds, six assists), Domantas Sabonis (35 points, 18 rebounds, 12 assists) and the Kings, 130-125. Eric Gordon added 23 points and four 3PM for the Suns in the victory. The Suns improve to 32-22 on the season, while the Kings fall to 30-23.
